Note.— The sample contains monthly observations from January 1982 to July 2001. \documentclass{aastex} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{bm} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{pifont} \usepackage{stmaryrd} \usepackage{textcomp} \usepackage{portland,xspace} \usepackage{amsmath,amsxtra} \usepackage[OT2,OT1]{fontenc} 
ewcommand\cyr{ enewcommandmdefault{wncyr} enewcommand\sfdefault{wncyss} enewcommand\encodingdefault{OT2} 
